#include<iostream>
#include<stdio.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
   int n,xl1,yl1,xu1,yu1,xl2,yl2,xu2,yu2;
   scanf("%d",&n);
   while(n--)
   {
         scanf("%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d",&xl1,&yl1,&xu1,&yu1,&xl2,&yl2,&xu2,&yu2);
         if(xl2-xl1<=(xu1-xl1) && yl2-yl1<=(yu1-yl1))
         printf("%d %d %d %d \n",xl2>xl1?xl2:xl1,yl2>yl1?yl2:yl1,xu1<xu2?xu1:xu2,yu1<yu2?yu1:yu2);
         else
         printf("No Overlap\n");
   }
}
